description:
Do you have an addiction? In the Bible it clearly states that all have sinned and we have all fallen short of the glory of God. Does that mean that we are all slaves and servants to our addictions? 


In this lecture, Dr. Diane Burnett examines habit formation in the brain, and how addiction can take hold in your mind. She explains the physiology of the brain and how everything we do leaves a mark on the mind. Learn why understanding addiction and the brain is the first step to taking control of our lives.
